  "elapsed_s": 124.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just because from mouth to mouth, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- and-- that's what I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were so nice though, like different people, not like the people from-- during the war, different people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were again-- before I met my husband-- before my husband, before we really got married, I stayed privately in a room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With a German in a German's house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nightmares all the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in all the time when we got together, we talked about the-- everybody talked about their life, how they survived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the only thing which kept us-- to be happy is that we saw the end of Hitler, that he-- we survived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he was going to kill all of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With Hitler, there will be no survivors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But somehow, thanks to God, there were survivors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he-- he didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we saw, like we say in Jewish, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The downfall from Hitler and Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
